Chapter 2 Be a Keyboard man

   2.1  Computer can do math
   
     1. Numerical 
  ------------------------------------------
  >>> 1+9
  >>> 1.3-4
  >>> 3*5
  >>> 4.5/1.5
  >>> 3**2
  >>> 10%3
  >>> "Vamei say:" + "Hello World"   # "Vamei say: Hello World!"
  >>> "Vamei" *2      # "VameiVamei"
  ------------------------------------------- 
    2. Logic
  Boolean:  true and false
  --------------------------------------------
  >>> True and True  # True
  >>> False and True  # False
  --------------------------------------------
  --------------------------------------------
  >>> True or True  # True
  >>> False or True  # True
  --------------------------------------------
  --------------------------------------------
  >>> not True  # False
  --------------------------------------------
     3. Judgment expression
  --------------------------------------------
  >>> 1==1  # true
  >>> 8.0 != 8.0
  >>> 3 < 5
  >>> 4 > 5
  >>> 4 >= 0
  --------------------------------------------
  
    4. Priority
  **   * /   + -   ==  >    >=   <   <=
  !  and  or 
  
